hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.element.base

Interface GuiElement<T extends GuiElement<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the class implementing this interface
    All Superinterfaces:
    AttachmentHolder<T>, DrawPrioritizeable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ButtonGuiElement, CheckboxGuiElement, ContinuousSliderGuiElement, DiscreteSliderGuiElement, DropdownGuiElement, GridGuiContainer, GuiContainer<T>, LinearGuiContainer, ProgressBarGuiElement, RadioButtonGuiElement, RectangleGuiElement, TextFieldGuiElement, TextGuiElement, TextureGuiElement

    public interface GuiElement<T extends GuiElement<T>>
extends AttachmentHolder<T>, DrawPrioritizeable<T>
    The base class for GUI elements. All other elements extend this class.

      • setPadding

        @NotNull
T setPadding(@NotNull
                      @NotNull int[] padding)
        Sets the padding values. The elements in the array must be the top, bottom, left, right padding values in this order. A value of -1 is allowed as a way to indicate to leave that specific padding value unchanged.
